@startuml
!theme plain
autonumber

actor "Shipping Agent Representative" as Rep
participant "User Interface\n(UI)" as UI
participant "Backend Service\n(Port System)" as Backend

Rep -> UI : 1: view submitted vessel visit notifications
activate UI
UI -> Backend : 1.1: Request (GetNotifications with filters)
activate Backend
Backend --> UI : 1.2: Response (List<VesselVisitNotificationDto>)
deactivate Backend
UI --> Rep : 1.3: Display filtered list with status, dock, and rejection reason
deactivate UI

@enduml
